title: Queer Beats - February 1, 2019
body:
This week on #QueerBeats, @glaad announced their media award nominees, #TCA19 brought lots of good queer news, and we finally got some new info about The L Word reboot!

Welcome back to Queer Beats, your weekly one-stop shop for queer television news! This week, GLAAD announced their media award nominees, the TCAs brought lots of good queer news, and we finally got some new info about The L Word reboot!

GLAAD Awards

title: i could get used to this
description:
by softvillaneve

Eve’s life is falling apart and she needs a change. So when she sees an ad for a job as a fire lookout, she figures that it’s just the thing to put a spark back in her life (pun intended). Will taking the job be her best decision, or her worst?

Firewatch AU - this is heavily inspired by the video game called Firewatch, which is one of my favorite games of all time. It’s not exactly necessary to have played/seen someone play the game before reading, as I’ll be trying to add enough detail to make it understandable, but I highly recommend watching someone’s playthrough if you have the time!
